kpi.name: M386B2C2

kpi_info.title: Long setup time is a PRFILE parameter which describes the time limit for the long call setups.
kpi_info.use: Long setup time is a PRFILE parameter which describes the time limit for the long call setups, that is, if the call setup time exceeds long setup time limit, it will be counted in M386B2C4 counter. The unit of time in ASCII report is seconds, in XML reports, it is 10 milliseconds.

kpi.kpi_alias: Long setup time is a PRFILE parameter which describes the time limit for the long call setups.
